			Live broadcast

Investment experts covering equities, fixed income, property and multi asset portfolios from global asset manager Aberdeen Asset Management are available to conduct broadcast interviews via the Globelynx network.
If you would like to book an interview please contact: press.office.uk@aberdeen-asset.com








