Aberdeen Asset Management plc (LON:ADN) PT Raised to GBX 285


					Posted by Joanna Charbonneau on Jul 23rd, 2017 // No Comments




Aberdeen Asset Management plc (LON:ADN) had its price objective upped by Barclays PLC from GBX 260 ($3.40) to GBX 285 ($3.72) in a research note released on Thursday. The brokerage currently has an underweight rating on the stock.
A number of other brokerages have also recently weighed in on ADN. BNP Paribas  reissued a neutral rating and set a GBX 300 ($3.92) price target on shares of Aberdeen Asset Management plc in a research report on Tuesday, July 18th. HSBC Holdings plc raised shares of Aberdeen Asset Management plc to a buy rating and lifted their price target for the stock from GBX 286 ($3.73) to GBX 350 ($4.57) in a research report on Friday, July 14th. Jefferies Group LLC lifted their price target on shares of Aberdeen Asset Management plc from GBX 287 ($3.75) to GBX 302 ($3.94) and gave the stock a hold rating in a research report on Tuesday, July 11th. Macquarie  reissued a neutral rating and set a GBX 271 ($3.54) price target on shares of Aberdeen Asset Management plc in a research report on Monday, May 15th. Finally, Berenberg Bank assumed coverage on shares of Aberdeen Asset Management plc in a research report on Thursday, June 15th. They set a hold rating and a GBX 290 ($3.79) price target on the stock. Four equities research analysts have rated the stock with a sell rating, eleven have issued  a hold rating and three have assigned  a buy rating to the company’s stock. Aberdeen Asset Management plc  has an average rating of Hold and an average target price of GBX 292.81 ($3.82).


 Get Aberdeen Asset Management plc alerts:



Aberdeen Asset Management plc (LON ADN) opened at 318.70 on Thursday. The stock has a 50 day moving average of GBX 300.01 and a 200-day moving average of GBX 281.54. The firm’s market capitalization is GBX 4.10 billion. Aberdeen Asset Management plc has a 1-year low of GBX 244.40 and a 1-year high of GBX 354.40. 
COPYRIGHT VIOLATION NOTICE: “Aberdeen Asset Management plc (LON:ADN) PT Raised to GBX 285” was  reported by Chaffey Breeze and is the property of of Chaffey Breeze. If you are accessing this story on another website, it was illegally copied and republished in violation of US & international copyright & trademark laws. The legal version of this story can be accessed at https://www.chaffeybreeze.com/2017/07/23/aberdeen-asset-management-plc-lonadn-pt-raised-to-gbx-285.html. 





Aberdeen Asset Management plc Company Profile
Aberdeen Asset Management PLC is a United Kingdom-based asset manager. The Company operates through asset management for reporting and control purposes. The Company is managed as a single asset management business, with multiple investment strategies of equities, fixed income and property, complemented by a solutions business, which provides multi asset, alternatives and quantitative investment capabilities.







